programme.title: Durga - Atut Prem Kahani
programme.sub-title: Durga and Anurag finally leaves inorder to treat Rukmini. Madhav and Anubhav too leaves with them. Anurag and Durga treats her and Rukmini gains consciousness. Everyone gets happy and Rukmini's parents blesses Durga. Anurag decides to talk to Durga and inform her about Pani bai's plan and asks madhav and Anubhav to meet them mid way and takes Durga along with him. He informs Durga about the plan and Durga gets scared . Anurag asks for a promise that she will not marry anyone but Durga is helpless and is unable to understand what to do. Anurag suggests to run away but Durga stops him from taking such step. Durga leaves with madhav and Anubhav and anurag thinks that he cannot see Durga with anyone else and wishes that Durga should be with him forever.
programme.desc: Durga - Atut Prem Kahani

programme.title: Suman Indori
programme.sub-title: Suman informs Bhoomi and Malini that Purna will give them the money before running out. Back at his home, Teerth confronts Kritika in front of his family for causing the accident. He tries to take her to the police but is stopped by Devika, who says he shouldn't trust Suman. Meanwhile, Suman reaches Purna's home and finds who she assumes is Purna. As she gets close, Gulshan reveals himself under his mother's dress. He assaults Suman, who fights back by breaking a vase on his head and throwing mirchi in his eyes. Purna walks in as Suman runs out. Devika reveals to Teerth's family that he is to marry Kritika, shocking everyone. She insults Suman while Teerth defends her. Chandrakant sides with Devika because of his hatred for Suman. Teerth questions how Kritika's car reached the accident site. Devika responds by asking Teerth and Kritika to follow her out. Teerth enters along with Kritika
programme.desc: Suman Indori

programme.title: Megha Barsenge
programme.sub-title: Megha speaks to her family on call telling them that they will come back to Amritsar. In the airport she gets a glimpse of Manoj and tells it to Arjun. Arjun catches him, but it turns out to be someone else. Megha lands India and gets horrified to see Manoj. He calls the media who questions Arjun about being involved with a mad woman like Megha. As Megha's parents arrive, they too get harrased by the media on grounds of their daughter being insane.

programme.title: Adapt To Survive
programme.sub-title: Episode Name: Cunning Opportunits : When it comes to finding food in the wild desperate times lead to desperate measures. When resources are sparse, it becomes every beast for themselves and stealing a meal is far easier than wasting energy pursuing one. This episode reveals how even the most skilled and ferocious hunters can stoop to common thievery when times are tough. Lions, jackals, hyenas, sharks and birds of prey are no stranger to the path of least resistance, and there are no fussy eaters in these parts - the only objective is securing their next meal.
programme.desc: When it comes to finding food in the wild desperate times lead to desperate measures

programme.title: Wild Odyssey
programme.sub-title: Episode Name: Scavengers : Humpback whales breach in New York's Hudson River. Huge colonies of megabats have made Adelaide their home. African Penguins find sanctuary and safe places to nest in Cape Town. Meet the extraordinary wildlife living in the fastest changing habitat on the planet - our cities. Animals have adjusted surprisingly well to city living. Not only are they applying their natural-born skills to this urban environment, they're also making amazing adaptations. Inspired by the Cities episode of Planet Earth II, this series explores our cities from a fresh perspective - through the eyes of the animals who live in them. Discover the wilder side of a world you think you know.
programme.desc: In the heart of the Mediterranean, there is a special world where bears and eagles live free among the vestiges of a distant past.

programme.title: Wild Africa: Rivers Of Life
programme.sub-title: Episode Name: Okavango Delta : In Northern Botswana lies the magnificent Okavango Delta; one of the most extraordinary ecosystems in Africa. In the heart of the Kalahari Desert, it's a wetland surrounded by parched and arid plains. The Delta and all the animals that live here, owe their very existence to the Okavango River. It delivers life-giving water to this area of flat, dry land; filling pools and swamps all year round. But, once a year, rain that falls a thousand miles away in Angola, creates an immense flood that overwhelms the swamps and spills over to the surrounding flood plains. The incredible oasis triples in size. Now the animals can indulge in a time of plenty.
programme.desc: In Northern Botswana lies the magnificent Okavango Delta; one of the most extraordinary ecosystems in Africa

programme.sub-title: Episode Name: The Queen Is Dead : The trouble with watching documentaries about lions is that males are so hopeless. In theory they protect the cubs from danger but in this first of a new series filmed in Zambia's Luangwa Valley, there's a scene where a male has been left in charge while the females hunt, and we watch as he decides to wander off, leaving the cubs at the mercy of an advancing herd of buffalo. Thanks a bunch, dad. There are other dramas as we follow a pride's private life, as well as the news that lionesses can plan, manipulate and deceive. Males, not so much.

programme.title: Little Krishna
programme.sub-title: Episode Name: Mystery Of The Vanishing Sheep, The : Little Krishna is the darling of Vrindavan, the land of peace and tranquility, which is constantly threatened by the malice of evil king Kamsa. In the past, a prophecy had threatened Kamsa that his evil reign is over, and a savior will descend on earth to make Kamsa meet his worst adversity in life, which is his death. programme.title: Super Bheem
programme.sub-title: Sky Dragon has received a signal for help from King Goliad's daughter Sonali of Grah Sona planet. There they meet Sonali, who tells them about evil Chumbak Dada who is after the planet's gold. Chumbak is controlling all the golids, including her father with his golden robots and making them dig up gold nuggets, which he plans to carry in his rocket. Bheem and his friends confront Chumbak.Bheem gets an idea and everyone follows his lead by quickly removing their any metallic items they might have been wearing. So when Chumbak sends more magnetic waves, he is unable to control them. Bheem catches hold of Chumbak's cape and swings him in circles and flings him. But Chumbak just smiles as huge golden robots are walking towards them.Bheem lifts the glass and holds it in front of him over the robots. The sunlight passes through the glass and exits as a concentrated hot beam of light. The robots' legs melt and they get stuck to the ground in a puddle of gold. Chumbak Dada falls into the molten gold.He is like a gold statue stuck in that pose. The golids and Bheem's friends start cheering.
programme.desc: Sky Dragon receives a distress signal from Sonali of Grah Sona, alerting him about the impending danger posed by the mischievous Chumbak Dada.
